OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening but staying largely dry.
OL,7,FLittle change overnight with cloudy
OL,8,Fconditions and the odd spot of rain.
OL,9,FLight northwesterly winds becoming
OL,10,Ffresh overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA little light rain possible
OL,13,Fin the morning otherwise mostly dry
OL,14,Fand cloudy day with a few brief bright
OL,15,Fintervals breaking through. Moderate
OL,16,Fto fresh northwesterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
