OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,6,Fcloudy few days with some bright or
OL,7,Fsunny intervals. Mostly dry but some
OL,8,Foutbreaks of light rain possible,
OL,9,Fespecially on Thursday. Moderate winds
OL,10,Fstrengthening on Thursday and Friday.
